text: National Highway 369E, commonly referred to as NH 369E is a national highway in India. It is a secondary route of National Highway 69. NH-369E runs in the state of Karnataka in India. == Route == NH369E connects Sagar, Huvinahalli, Holebaglu, Kalasavalli, Sighanadoor and Markutuka in the state of Karnataka. == Junctions == : Terminal near Sagar. : Terminal near Markutuka. == See also == * List of National Highways in India * List of National Highways in India by state == References == == External links == * NH 369E on OpenStreetMap Category:National highways in India Category:National Highways in Karnataka
